00:06:59.481 --> 00:07:00.681
Kelas!

00:07:00.876 --> 00:07:01.976
Beri hormat.

00:07:02.057 --> 00:07:03.676
Terima kasih, cikgu.

00:07:24.133 --> 00:07:25.633
Kacaknya.

00:07:25.966 --> 00:07:27.266
Siapa?

00:07:29.179 --> 00:07:30.679
Pelajar baru itu?

00:07:32.441 --> 00:07:34.659
Entahlah. Saya tak rasa dia kacak pun.

00:07:34.740 --> 00:07:38.252
Hei, cuba tengok
budak lelaki kelas kita ini.

00:07:38.348 --> 00:07:39.462
Ada yang kacak macam dia?

00:07:39.543 --> 00:07:40.943
Mestilah ada!

00:07:41.024 --> 00:07:42.200
Siapa?

00:07:43.552 --> 00:07:44.552
