00:08:12.305 --> 00:08:15.072
Kang Junsang. Dia milik saya!

00:08:15.389 --> 00:08:16.989
Kamu jangan memikat dia.

00:08:26.215 --> 00:08:29.015
Apa khabar? Saya Oh Chaerin.
Gembira berjumpa kamu.

00:08:38.264 --> 00:08:39.264
Kasihan dia.

00:08:42.484 --> 00:08:43.729
Helo.

00:08:43.810 --> 00:08:45.110
Saya Kim Sanghyuk.

00:08:45.233 --> 00:08:47.233
Selamat berkenalan.

00:08:52.940 --> 00:08:54.996
Awak perlu sertai kelab di sekolah ini.

00:08:55.182 --> 00:08:56.622
Awak berminat dengan kelab tertentu?

00:08:57.513 --> 00:08:58.713
Saya tak berminat.

00:09:02.324 --> 00:09:03.362
Kang Junsang!

00:09:03.506 --> 00:09:04.906
Beri pada saya.
Saya akan tanya dia.

00:09:11.133 --> 00:09:12.797
Hei.

00:09:13.133 --> 00:09:14.633
Hei, Kang Junsang!

00:09:18.407 --> 00:09:21.336
Awak tak patut buat begini
pada hari pertama di kelas.

00:09:21.429 --> 00:09:23.229
Awak dah menyusahkan ketua kelas.

00:09:23.404 --> 00:09:25.004
Awak nak sertai kelab apa?

00:09:26.633 --> 00:09:28.037
Awak tak tidur di sekolah?

00:09:28.251 --> 00:09:29.251
Apa?

00:09:33.733 --> 00:09:36.133
Awak dari sekolah sains dulu.

00:09:36.214 --> 00:09:37.477
Apa kata awak sertai Kelab Sains?

00:09:37.543 --> 00:09:40.343
Pernah awak tengok pemain besbol
