00:10:40.543 --> 00:10:42.994
-Semalam masih elok.
-Aduhai.

00:10:43.252 --> 00:10:45.226
Ini mesti sebab awak, Chaerin!

00:10:45.307 --> 00:10:46.926
Bukan sebab sayalah!

00:10:47.033 --> 00:10:49.273
Benda itu memang dah bermasalah
sebelum saya sentuh lagi.

00:10:49.832 --> 00:10:50.954
Mungkin...

00:10:51.105 --> 00:10:53.747
...suis dah tercabut?

00:10:54.102 --> 00:10:57.669
Jinsook, jangan sentuh apa-apa.
Nanti lagi teruk.

