-Turunlah.
-Tak nak!

00:13:28.688 --> 00:13:30.005
Hari ini...

00:13:30.537 --> 00:13:32.833
...saya nak jalan sampai hujung sana!

00:13:32.933 --> 00:13:34.658
Awak tak lepas 10 langkah pun.

00:13:34.739 --> 00:13:36.612
Awak tengoklah saya boleh atau tak!

00:13:37.731 --> 00:13:38.752
Lima.

00:13:39.106 --> 00:13:41.709
-Enam!
-Berhati-hati.

00:13:41.833 --> 00:13:44.333
Yoojin, pegang tangan saya.

00:13:44.631 --> 00:13:45.726
Tak nak.

00:13:45.807 --> 00:13:47.407
Saya bukan teman wanita awak.

00:13:47.488 --> 00:13:50.162
Kenapa saya nak pegang tangan awak?

00:13:50.671 --> 00:13:53.725
Hanya orang yang istimewa saja...

00:13:53.979 --> 00:13:55.933
...boleh pegang tangan saya.

00:13:59.533 --> 00:14:01.133
Awak nampak tak?

00:14:32.176 --> 00:14:34.476
"Kang Mihee"

00:14:45.847 --> 00:14:47.099
"Kim Jinwoo"

00:14:59.195 --> 00:15:00.495
Kamu semua faham?

00:15:00.595 --> 00:15:02.014
Faham.

00:15:02.095 --> 00:15:05.395
Saya ulang sekali lagi.

00:15:06.595 --> 00:15:08.695
Saya akan padamkannya.

00:15:09.595 --> 00:15:11.495
Prof, jangan padam!

00:15:11.695 --> 00:15:12.595
Nanti dulu!

00:15:12.695 --> 00:15:13.995
Jangan padam.

00:15:14.084 --> 00:15:15.351
Kenapa padamkannya?

00:15:20.711 --> 00:15:23.813
Saya nak kamu faham dan bukan
sekadar mencatat dan menghafal.

00:15:24.012 --> 00:15:26.948
Kamu boleh cari formula di dalam buku.

00:15:27.042 --> 00:15:28.771
Perkara paling penting
perlu diingat dalam matematik...

00:15:28.837 --> 00:15:32.447
...bukanlah formula atau penjelasan
masalah yang telah diselesaikan,...

00:15:32.642 --> 00:15:34.069
...tapi rasa ingin tahu dan imaginasi.

00:15:34.135 --> 00:15:37.595
Saya nak kamu cuba bayangkan
di papan hitam ini.

00:15:38.875 --> 00:15:41.232
Sekarang masa untuk menjawab soalan.

00:15:41.484 --> 00:15:42.884
Siapa nak cuba?

00:15:53.431 --> 00:15:54.631
Pelajar itu.

00:15:57.753 --> 00:15:59.478
Apa kata kamu cuba?

00:16:09.215 --> 00:16:11.733
Saya cuma nak tahu jika
kamu faham formula.

00:16:11.814 --> 00:16:13.414
Jangan rasa tertekan.

